{"tid":2449531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"俞定延個賤種幾時減肥？","createTime":"2021-03-16T17:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T05:46:17.000Z","uid":37146,"like":14,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c2b33fb441e65581d43582ef88a89aa07f4e2c0d","tid":2449531,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:48:37.000Z","msg":"攪撚到CRY FOR ME呢首咁正個歌拍唔到MV<br />\n明明有個好機會俾T寶反彈一波，難得有首好歌<br />\n就係呢隻肥閪拖累晒，之前幾年已經係老鼠屎<br />\n個時南南FEEL SPECIAL時期都病緊，一樣頂硬上照拍MV，好感人之餘仲依然靚到仆街<br />\n最後，慢慢歸隊，對團隊無大影響，T寶人氣依舊火熱<br />\n<br />\n上年出左兩首垃圾，風格戇鳩，隻舞冇重點，又難聽到爆，令到T寶人氣明顯有下滑，雖然都係世一女團，但俾BP追近左好多<br />\n去到年尾有首編舞好正，歌又好聽既CRY FOR ME，點知俾隻肥閪阻住晒，做唔知攪乜肥到豬咁，好心快撚啲做運動又好，學隊長志效抽脂又好，快啲撚歸隊，咪撚阻住地球轉，錯過左都唔人氣彈唔彈得返起，屌你老母"},{"pid":"2389cc11e547a9c1bd3d546325874d42e3529d80","tid":2449531,"uid":384468,"like":20,"dislike":15,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"點睇Ros&eacute;訓係度都屌打T寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://kpopping.com/documents/d3/3/1100/210314-ROSE-at-SBS-Inkigayo-GONE-ON-THE-GROUND-Solo-Debut-documents-15.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkpopping.com%2Fdocuments%2Fd3%2F3%2F1100%2F210314-ROSE-at-SBS-Inkigayo-GONE-ON-THE-GROUND-Solo-Debut-documents-15.jpeg&h=dfccf921&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe2cf86d7130f3dc4adf60c20c00938062b1f048","tid":2449531,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2389cc11e547a9c1bd3d546325874d42e3529d80","tid":2449531,"uid":384468,"like":20,"dislike":15,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"點睇Ros&eacute;訓係度都屌打T寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://kpopping.com/documents/d3/3/1100/210314-ROSE-at-SBS-Inkigayo-GONE-ON-THE-GROUND-Solo-Debut-documents-15.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkpopping.com%2Fdocuments%2Fd3%2F3%2F1100%2F210314-ROSE-at-SBS-Inkigayo-GONE-ON-THE-GROUND-Solo-Debut-documents-15.j